lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沖涼洗個靚頭係必須<br />\n我嗰個起碼都會話自己個頭吹衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7040136bdd7117a7e65561bf9b3e9d9d8f02cb","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"39be17a9157f0c9d27a396b69e386cf2e24a6e65","tid":2351991,"uid":117344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"未溝到先會落力打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"溝到之後唔會擔心女朋友比第二個搶走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我以前拍拖見到佢身邊啲靚女 再諗自己唔打扮嗰樣 會好擔心男朋友比第二個溝走"},{"pid":"5c204d9a32b5a81665f191d9911c2e9b909c4858","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2a03c2cc0335ed8e149873f570e761bc65998f09","tid":2351991,"uid":142522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"07d786bf4118d44e2cc393772fdc9b93ab781d7d","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bbea0d0fbe3d8dd73b86cde61df818c56d335b0d","tid":2351991,"uid":142522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"男朋友都成日唔剃鬚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都慣咗，一齊耐咗兩個人都唔會特別執到正<br />\n有時真係冇咁多時間（我同佢都好難夾時間見）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"其實間唔時緊係冇所謂<br />\n我又唔係要佢日日執到好靚仔<br />\n<br />\n但係次次去街都唔執下就會有啲介意 唔剃鬚都洗頭啦<br />\n有次見到好多頭皮好尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"唔係掛，頭皮都有埋，咁就過分咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沖涼洗個靚頭係必須<br />\n我嗰個起碼都會話自己個頭吹衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係要佢執到好正 只係想佢有啲基本清潔 個人衛生嚟<br />\n<br />\n諗返自己見佢之前又洗頭又化妝又襯衫搞勁耐 嗰陣見到佢咁hea都有啲氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d3ca892903456edc6b648c4e2667912e6c6762","tid":2351991,"uid":24607,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"其實我落街買餸都執到正先落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以見親啲ex都係着最肆正<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非hungover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ad4a4667eae6aa4a6ace0c511ec0931c2402b1","tid":2351991,"uid":347070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0218d844a3f2a37478569ab5d857739a2392566b","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"之前好鍾意條仔 佢做乜我都覺得冇咩問題<br />\n幾邋遢幾&rdquo;哩啡&rdquo;都唔會話太介意<br />\n但係最近清醒咗 就睇得清楚曬<br />\n突然之間出現咗一種&rdquo;呀 點解當初會鍾意佢&rdquo;嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經唔係外表嘅問題<br />\n而係基本個人清潔都唔做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初我都可以視而不見<br />\n係咪盲撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論男女都好 對住另一半定係曖昧對象都好<br />\n有時真係唔好太頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能有啲人會話就係俾對方睇自己最真實嘅一面<br />\n但係我覺得有陣時 着得好睇啲對方都會開心啲 冇咁容易厭 基本打扮或者個人清潔係尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:57:11.000Z","msg":"對住鐘意個嗰 佢影肚腩比我 我都覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db7233d0be790d74a6b3d8b8fb01d2db249f070","tid":2351991,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T19:23:31.000Z","msg":"所以我出街前會洗屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左防止突發性要俾人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f4c1ecc9a901d85367260c108eeb4e1f3bb433","tid":2351991,"uid":179990,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e691c9ab112b423615e82e263a58cfdc8367cb6c","tid":2351991,"uid":127929,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T19:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29cd0d9b847b50c26194822fe679206775fe8b","tid":2351991,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T21:31:23.000Z","msg":"情淫眼裡出西先"},{"pid":"db7ce6191958af1c1981777f117619a331c7b80a","tid":2351991,"uid":334200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1087b1d858c390d4ee96d2780bcfb71f7f1f5900","tid":2351991,"uid":62841,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"1ffdd8ed6728ab4364fcaaffa05a4c8489bf5ffd","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5883770ce3931d76e35dddf40d7c06a7ffe58d4a","tid":2351991,"uid":62841,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"對街外人先要執正個樣<br />\n見女朋友有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強加自己套價值落人地度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"咁你依家咪都係強加自己套價值觀喺人地度<br />\n逼人地接受你頹look唔打扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你女朋友次次同你出街唔化妝唔洗頭著到成個阿嬸咁樣你得唔得？你會唔會完全唔會將佢同街出面啲女仔做比較？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"依家係你要求你男朋友喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關我撚事<br />\n你問我咁我老實答<br />\n我真係prefer女朋友頹look 但我冇迫佢要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你只係個垃圾控制狂臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:53:19.000Z","msg":"以往被濾鏡遮蔽咗嘅一面，當濾鏡隨感情而破爛，對方嘅好多缺點自然會被無限放大。感情已經過去，唔好回頭啦。只會令自己心情唔好，冇好處。"},{"pid":"bd2ed6573b51f334978146285e2d56797d66886f","tid":2351991,"uid":202351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:56:18.000Z","msg":"屌 垃圾港女 拉"},{"pid":"5056b5f6d480acb5721fe9345744744bbe718b7e","tid":2351991,"uid":206008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a03c2cc0335ed8e149873f570e761bc65998f09","tid":2351991,"uid":142522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"07d786bf4118d44e2cc393772fdc9b93ab781d7d","tid":2351991,"uid":305839,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bbea0d0fbe3d8dd73b86cde61df818c56d335b0d","tid":2351991,"uid":142522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"男朋友都成日唔剃鬚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都慣咗，一齊耐咗兩個人都唔會特別執到正<br />\n有時真係冇咁多時間（我同佢都好難夾時間見）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"其實間唔時緊係冇所謂<br />\n我又唔係要佢日日執到好靚仔<br />\n<br />\n但係次次去街都唔執下就會有啲介意 唔剃鬚都洗頭啦<br />\n有次見到好多頭皮好尷尬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"唔係掛，頭皮都有埋，咁就過分咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沖涼洗個靚頭係必須<br />\n我嗰個起碼都會話自己個頭吹衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:56:35.000Z","msg":"有啲人洗完頭都會有頭皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" 